[[File:CIA-map-of-borders-of-Nepal-1965.jpg|thumb]]
'''中國－尼泊爾邊界'''是中國[[西藏自治區|西藏自治區]]與[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]]的邊界，全長1389公里，以西北-東南方向[[喜馬拉雅山脈|喜馬拉雅山脈]]而行，包括世界最高山[[珠穆朗瑪峰|珠穆朗瑪峰]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Nepal |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/resources/the-world-factbook/geos/np.html |publisher=CIA World Factbook |accessdate=23 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905125921/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/resources/the-world-factbook/geos/np.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此邊界隨時間不斷改變。1956年《中尼友好協議》和1960年《{{link-en|中尼和平友好條約|Sino-Nepalese Treaty of Peace and Friendship}}》的簽訂後，尼泊爾承認西藏為中國領土，並確認了中尼兩國的範圍<ref>{{cite book |last1=Van Tronder |first1=Gerry |title=Sino-Indian War: Border Clash: October–November 1962 |date=2018 |publisher=Pen and Sword Military |isbn=9781526728388 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JrTNDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT12&lpg=PT12&dq=sino-indian+war+patrols+at+Ladakh+april+30+1962#v=onepage |access-date=2020-10-15 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020223023/https://books.google.com/books?id=JrTNDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT12&lpg=PT12&dq=sino-indian%20war%20patrols%20at%20Ladakh%20april%2030%201962#v=onepage |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Adhikari |first1=Monalisa |title=Between the Dragon and the Elephant: Nepal's Neutrality Conundrum |journal=Indian Journal of Asian Affairs |date=2012 |volume=25 |issue=1/2 |page=85 |jstor=41950522 }}</ref>。

== 概覽 ==
[[File:Mount_Everest_North_Face.jpg|thumb]]
邊界由[[遠西省|遠西省]]近{{link-en|亭加山口|Tinkar Pass}}與[[印度|印度]]的西端三角點開始<ref>{{citation |first=Sam |last=Cowan |authorlink=Samuel Cowan |title=The Indian checkposts, Lipu Lekh, and Kalapani |publisher=School of Oriental and African Studies |date=2015 |url=https://digital.soas.ac.uk/SWAY000513/00001 |pp=16–17 |accessdate=2020-10-15 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203102353/https://digital.soas.ac.uk/SWAY000513/00001 |dead-url=no }}</ref>向東南到烏拉山口，轉向東北，並沿[[格爾納利河|格爾納利河]]而行，在拉普齊山口轉向東南。之後再前往喜瑪拉雅山脈的山峰前進，包括[[珠穆朗瑪峰|珠穆朗瑪峰]]、[[馬卡魯峰|馬卡魯峰]]及{{link-en|戈乃斯山|Salasungo}}，以及一系列山口<ref name="IBS"/>，並以[[瓊桑峰|瓊桑峰]]的東端三角點結束<ref name="IBS"/>。

== 歷史 ==
邊界範圍向來都是尼泊爾、印度和西藏等王國的邊緣地帶<ref name="IBS"/>。尼泊爾和西藏的跨境貿易已持續幾個世紀，包括[[羊毛|羊毛]]、[[茶|茶]]、[[香辛料|香料]]及[[鹽|鹽]]<ref name="murton_crosscurrent">{{Cite magazine
